"{\"uid\": \"kbzk.com-news-local-news-manhattan-marksman-going-for-gold-in-shooting-at-the-2024-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"MANHATTAN - At just seven years old, Ivan Roe's father signed him up for a gun safety and hunter's education class.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 115, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fast forward to today, and he's getting ready to compete in the 2024 Olympic Games in competitive shooting.\", \"from\": 116, \"to\": 223, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Coming all the way from Manhattan, Ivan says it's the opportunity of a lifetime.\", \"from\": 224, \"to\": 304, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 248, \"end\": 257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.982167047776057, \"rank\": 0.018156738103945746, \"text\": \"Manhattan\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's pretty much a pinnacle achievement of your life, something you might not ever be able to do again,\\\" said Roe.\", \"from\": 306, \"to\": 421, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Growing up in the small-town atmosphere of Manhattan with less than 50 people in his graduating class, Ivan Roe has big dreams.\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 550, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 466, \"end\": 475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.982167047776057, \"rank\": 0.018156738103945746, \"text\": \"Manhattan\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There were definitely times where I thought, \\\"well, what if I make it-it would be cool to be the first Olympian from Manhattan,\\\" said Roe.\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 691, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 656, \"end\": 664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999933353525821, \"rank\": 6.6511630533390635e-06, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 670, \"end\": 679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.982167047776057, \"rank\": 0.018156738103945746, \"text\": \"Manhattan\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For several years, Roe set out on a mission to earn his spot on Team USA in competitive shooting.\", \"from\": 693, \"to\": 790, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 757, \"end\": 765, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9754157170990149, \"rank\": 0.01916586508478255, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not want to put it down,\\\" said Roe.\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 834, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wanted to keep going and see what I could do.\\\"\", \"from\": 835, \"to\": 884, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After countless matches, multiple international titles, and even joining the U.S. Army, Sergeant Ivan Roe earned his ticket to the Olympics after completing USA Shooting's three-part Rifle Olympic Trials against 77 other top marksmen from across the United States.\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 1150, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 968, \"end\": 972, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Army\", \"score\": 0.9999994052470306, \"rank\": 5.446682026505811e-07, \"text\": \"Army\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Army\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Army\"}, {\"begin\": 974, \"end\": 982, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sergeant\", \"score\": 0.8615594467669179, \"rank\": 0.1591455727422417, \"text\": \"Sergeant\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sergeant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sergeant\"}, {\"begin\": 1043, \"end\": 1055, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Shooting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USA Shooting\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Shooting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Shooting\"}, {\"begin\": 1075, \"end\": 1089, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Olympic_trials_(track_and_field)\", \"score\": 0.8581582794952675, \"rank\": 0.03896103896103429, \"text\": \"Olympic Trials\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Olympic_trials_(track_and_field)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Olympic_trials_(track_and_field)\"}, {\"begin\": 1136, \"end\": 1149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.999798076672258, \"rank\": 7.737825778217129e-05, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He says he's still in awe of the accomplishment.\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1200, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I remember my hands, my face-my whole body tingling,\\\" said Roe.\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1266, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I went out to my car and just cried tears of relief that I finally did it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1343, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Roe attributes a lot of his success to his dad, who he says unintentionally led him to his passion.\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1444, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not think at the beginning he ever thought I'd take it this far,\\\" said Roe.\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1527, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He did not enroll me in the BB gun program so I could become an Olympian.\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1602, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1557, \"end\": 1563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BB_gun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BB gun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BB_gun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BB_gun\"}, {\"begin\": 1593, \"end\": 1601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999933353525821, \"rank\": 6.6511630533390635e-06, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He enrolled me so I could become a safe hunter.\\\"\", \"from\": 1603, \"to\": 1651, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But even so, Sgt.\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1670, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Roe says his dad has been one of his biggest supporters.\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1727, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He's been with me every step of the way, watching and rooting for me,\\\" said Roe.\", \"from\": 1729, \"to\": 1810, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In July, Roe's father will be on a plane to the Paris Summer Olympics to watch his son go for Gold.\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1911, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Being able to put my name on the list of people who have worn the Montana flag and competed proudly for the state is something I look forward to,\\\" said Roe.\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 2070, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1980, \"end\": 1987, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montana\", \"score\": 0.9987841975686247, \"rank\": 0.0009151804969840216, \"text\": \"Montana\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More Local News from KBZK  Gabrielle Cleveland    Cassidy Powers    Cassidy Powers    MTN News    MTN News    Cassidy Powers    Gabrielle Cleveland    Meghan Elaine\", \"from\": 2072, \"to\": 2236, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2158, \"end\": 2161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MTN_Group\", \"score\": 0.9998487757104754, \"rank\": 0.00015124716045486781, \"text\": \"MTN\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MTN_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MTN_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 2200, \"end\": 2209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabrielle_Drake\", \"score\": 0.9999757035005014, \"rank\": 2.429708893154811e-05, \"text\": \"Gabrielle\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabrielle_Drake\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabrielle_Drake\"}, {\"begin\": 2210, \"end\": 2219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cleveland_Brown\", \"score\": 0.986157181900962, \"rank\": 0.014035824058813262, \"text\": \"Cleveland\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cleveland_Brown\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cleveland_Brown\"}]}]}"